    <dc:title>Building Embodied AI: From Perception to Autonomous Action</dc:title>
    <dc:creator id="creator_00">Alexander Apartsin</dc:creator>
    <dc:creator id="creator_01">Yehudit Aperstein</dc:creator>
    <dc:description>A comprehensive hands-on guide to building embodied AI systems, from robotics foundations and perception to reinforcement learning, robot data, world models, safety, deployment, capstones, and course design.</dc:description>
